Ever Decreasing Circles[1984-1989]

Martin is a committee man. He has numerous schemes and committees organised around the neighbourhood. He is so obsessive about every detail of everything he does he is driving his long suffering wife, Anne, slowly crazy. Then the new neighbour Paul arrives. He has a more worldly outlook than those who live under Martin's organisational spell.

Hilarious 80s comedy starring the late Richard Briers, rip taken from my own box set dvds.
